snippet.title: RAN: Lost Islands - Beta Test Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/986220/RAN_Lost_Islands/

RAN: Lost Islands is an online multiplayer combat game set in the 16th Century era of melee weapons and firearms. 100 challengers play as outcasts, battling to survive as they experience the age of discovery and seek a magnificent ancient treasure.

Sign up for Beta Access: www.playlostislands.com
Follow us on Twitter @PlayLostIslands
Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/chP9JGu
